31899.text: [31899] StaticText "ALL INCLUSIVE PAINT SET: Unleash your creativity from beginner to professional level with this fun and educational acrylic paint. Open the box, and you're ready to draw and paint! It comes complete with 24 vibrant paints in 60ml bottles, providing ample colors for your artistic endeavors. Additionally, we've included 12 high-quality acrylic paint brushes, catering to both kids and adults."

31904.text: [31904] StaticText "PREMIUM VIBRANT COLORS: Our paint delivers brilliance, gliding on smoothly and drying quickly, preserving their vibrant shades. Whether you're an amateur or a pro, the 24 colors in this set will fuel your creativity. Perfect for canvas art, these fade-resistant colors ensure your work lasts. Achieve consistent shades and let your creativity flourish with this exceptional paint kit."

31909.text: [31909] StaticText "VIVID COLORS, SAFE & EASY CLEANUP: Immerse yourself in a world of rich, vibrant pigments worry-free with our acrylic paint set. It's non-toxic and adheres to ASTM D4236 safety standards. Experience seamless blending and quick drying. Our fast-drying formula enables immediate layering and creative exploration. When it's time to tidy up, a simple wash with soap and water effortlessly clears your workspace."
